* [[吉勒摩·戴托羅|吉勒摩·戴托羅]]執導的[[2006年電影|2006年電影]]《[[羊男的迷宮|羊男的迷宮]]》中，一個人羊引導著故事主角奧菲莉亞（Ofelia）完成一系列的任務<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/pans-labyrinth-review-2006-movie-1070658|title='Pan's Labyrinth': THR's 2006 Review|newspaper=The Hollywood Reporter|accessdate=2018-03-16|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211183919/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/pans-labyrinth-review-2006-movie-1070658|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.shmoop.com/pans-labyrinth/faun.html|title=Faun (Doug Jones) in Pan's Labyrinth|accessdate=2018-03-16|work=www.shmoop.com|language=en|archive-date=2018-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180317102140/https://www.shmoop.com/pans-labyrinth/faun.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

